<div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <br>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag "profile2.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img'%>
              <div class="skills">
                <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                  <div class="skill">
                  <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                  <div class="progress">
                    <div
                      class="progess-bar progress-bar-striped bg-info"
                      role="progressbar"
                      aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                      aria-valuemax="100"
                      style="width: <%=skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                    ></div>
                  </div>                  
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>

            <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>Technology wasn't that path I thought I was going on, but I am sure glad I did!
                   Being a creative person I have always wanted to shared my ideas in as many ways as possible!
                   Lucky for me web development is one of the most creative outlets. Building and Designing something
                   that my client will use years to come is my source of motivation. Its not just nerding out because my website is communicating with twitter,
                   check that out on the "Tech News" page. It is making functional and gorgeous websites for everyone!</p>
              

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-outline-default"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-outline-default"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Smith's Food and Drug - Cashier
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Free Lance Photographer
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              American International School of Utah
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bottega Tech
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

